[div class=p 
	"I got hit a few times throughout the game:
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	[b 
		"Marble Garden 1
	]b
	" - Spikeball was in the way and I didn't want to wait for it to move.
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	[b 
		"Launch Base 1
	]b
	" - Needed to lose the Lightning Shield to beat the boss faster.
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	[b 
		"Sandopolis 2
	]b
	" - Let a ghost hit me so I could land on top of a rock without breaking it. The extra height makes it possible to reach the platform above by bouncing off the ring boxes, avoiding a really long wait for the sand to catch up.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"This was mostly recorded at 6% speed so I could perform spindashes at full power in the shortest time possible, and so that jumps could be timed perfectly to gain the most height and/or speed. On many occasions I tried each jump several times, timing it a frame or so earlier or later just to find the optimal position :)
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"I can't see this run being improved by much without some additional shortcuts being found and used...
	$LF
]div
